{
  "stem": "15174.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they-- they really, they treated us well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Food was a big problem because the Germans were requisitioning all the food that they could get for Germany and for the German Army.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, we were in a village which was very helpful, because food was being produced right there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you know, they had a certain quota.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had to send food to Paris and to the German Army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There wasn't much left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, a lot of it they kept to feed themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to buy it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, how do we get any money?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when they found out that my father was a tailor, they asked him to-- to-- to work, because there was no tailor for miles around, or I should say kilometers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, well, I can't work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't have a sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So one of the people in the village had a sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She gave it to my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He set up shop and he-- he was working, and it really was-- was terrific because we had some money. you weren't able to get much for that money, but we had some.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And yeah, so food was a problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We really-- there was very little food to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, my mother would go and buy some bread, and rarely, I guess, we would have maybe an egg or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean-- and vegetables.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there wasn't a lot to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I-- [LAUGH] I remember, it was, I guess, the-- the Rosh Hashanah after we actually-- no.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There must have been two Rosh Hashanahs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It must have been 1941.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My mother was saying we're going to have a holiday, and we don't have-- we really don't have any food.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
